The head nun gathered all the nuns of the abbey and asked:
- My daughters, if you have seen a man's penis, raise your hand.
One nun raises her hand. The senior nun told her:
- Come to me, my daughter, sanctify your eyes with holy water and you will be forgiven. And now, raise your hand, who held the penis in his hands.
The other nun raised her hand. The senior nun told her:
- Come to me, my daughter, wash your hands and you will be forgiven.
Some nun from the crowd:
- Can I rinse my mouth?
- No one has washed their ass yet...
